parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time of day represented as milliseconds after 00:00:00.000

parameters.name: MASS_NUM
parameters.description:
Mass Number:                              
                        4 for He
                        14 for N
                        16 for O
                        28 for N2
                        29 for CO
                        44 for CO2

parameters.name: FLAG
parameters.description:
Flag:                                     
                        0 for fully corrected                           
                        1 for preliminary (not fully corrected)                     
                        2 for mass flagged (problem point; probably wrong)                                   
                        3 for final density negative (only preliminary density given)
